parameters.name: BX
parameters.description:
J3 X component of the magnetic-field component in nT.                   
      X is in the Jovian equatorial plane along the line through the          
      System 3 (1997), positive away from Jupiter.

parameters.name: BY
parameters.description:
J3 Y component of the magnetic field component in nT.                   
      Y completes the right handed set (Z x X).

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description:
J3 Z component of the magnetic field component in nT.                   
      Z is parallel to Jovian spin axis, Omega, positive north of             
      the equator.
